text: Medvedyorovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 90 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Kushnarenkovo, 24 km from Akhmetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Medvedyorovo
